<h1>Informations</h1>

<p>Welcome to Crowd Bet</p>
<p>You can vote on different questions/events during the game and collect points. For this purpose there are different types of questions</p>
<p>Type 1:<br />For every correct answer you get 1 point</p>
<p>Type 2:<br />You can bet your earned points and if the answer is correct, you will get your investet points- but if your answer is wrong, you will lose the bet points.</p>
<p>Type 3:<br />ALL IN - You bet all your points - big risk but also big profit. With the correct answer you can double your score.</p>
<p>Be attentive and fast, you don't have all the time in the world to answer the questions.</p>
